	<h1 class="title">86 张图片，告诉你快要过去的2015年所有值得纪念的时刻</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3121/small/3121.jpg?1440471388" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Steven Erlanger</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-23 12:26:26 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19562/medium/19562.jpg?1450857599" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


