<h1>
	十二月
</h1>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<span><strong></strong></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<strong><img src="/uploads/image/201512/45e256beaa29.jpg" width="1024" height="683" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span></strong> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<strong>加州圣博纳蒂诺</strong>&nbsp;<strong>2015&nbsp;</strong><strong>年&nbsp;</strong><strong>12&nbsp;</strong><strong>月&nbsp;</strong><strong>7&nbsp;</strong><strong>日</strong> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span>人们秉烛守夜，以纪念被一对激进派穆斯林夫妇枪击身亡的 </span><span>14 </span><span>名遇难者。</span>图片来源：Monica Almeida / 《纽约时报》
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<span><strong></strong></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<strong><img src="/uploads/image/201512/9067d90dcc51.jpg" width="1024" height="683" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span></strong> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<strong>北京</strong>&nbsp;<strong>2015&nbsp;</strong><strong>年&nbsp;</strong><strong>12&nbsp;</strong><strong>月&nbsp;</strong><strong>8&nbsp;</strong><strong>日</strong> 
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<span>在中国首都第一次发布空气污染</span><span>“</span><span>红色预警</span><span>”</span><span>后，学校被关闭、驾车受到了限制，工厂也被停工。</span>图片来源：Damir Sagoli / 路透社
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/0bcfdf58e4b0.jpg" width="1024" height="683" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<div style="text-align:center;">
	<strong>华盛顿 2015 </strong><strong>年 </strong><strong>12 </strong><strong>月 </strong><strong>12 </strong><strong>日</strong> 
</div>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<span>白宫内阁会议室中的讲台，奥巴马在那里宣布了由 </span><span>195 </span><span>个国家签署的一份历史性协议，以减少温室气体的排放。</span>图片来源：Doug Mills / 《纽约时报》
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201512/a6080204dce2.jpg" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span> 
</p>
<div style="text-align:center;">
	<strong>拉斯维加斯 2015 年 12 月 9 日</strong> 
</div>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<span>光背马骑手波比</span><span>·</span><span>莫特（</span><span>Bobby Mote</span><span>）在参加全美牛仔竞技总决赛（</span><span>National Finals Rodeo</span><span>）。这是牛仔运动项目的顶极赛事。<span>图片来源：</span></span>Josh Haner / 《纽约时报》
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span><strong></strong></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<strong><img src="/uploads/image/201512/65c04248d54f.jpg" width="1024" height="684" title=" " alt=" " /><span> </span></strong> 
</p>
<div style="text-align:center;">
	<strong><span><strong>纽约布鲁克林 </strong></span><span><strong>2015 </strong></span><span><strong>年 </strong></span><span><strong>12 </strong></span><span><strong>月 </strong></span><span><strong>7 </strong></span><span><strong>日</strong></span></strong> 
</div>
<p>
</p>
<p>
	<span>为纪念光明节，莱布</span><span>·</span><span>科尔曼（</span><span>Leib Kelman</span><span>）在他位于肯辛顿社区的家门外点燃烛台。</span>图片来源：Todd Heisler / 《纽约时报》
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span>翻译 熊猫译社 葛仲君 刘昉</span> 
</p>
